==English==

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}
#Feeling [[pain]] or [[sorrow]] on account of [[sin]]s or offenses; [[repentant]]; [[contrite]]; sincerely affected by a sense of guilt, and resolved on amendment of life.
#Doing [[penance]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
#One who [[repent]]s of sin; one sorrowful on account of his transgressions.
#One under church [[censure]], but admitted to [[penance]]; one undergoing penance.
#One under the direction of a [[confessor]].

